# Shot-only automation

User-facing happy path: **enter MAST shot number → get FreeGSNKE results**.

When changing CLI, interactive launcher, configs, or pipeline stages:

- Do not add new required prompts in the happy path
- Default config must enable download + extract + generate + execute + metrics when authorities exist
- Missing authority → fail with a clear blocking error and fix hint, never invent metrology
- Prefer wiring existing authorities (`coil_map`, contracts, execution_authority) over new heuristic paths
